FT  15 JAN 92 / UK Company News: Debenham Tewson declines to Pounds 727,000
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The continuing recession in the property market hit industry advisers
Debenham Tewson &amp; Chinnocks, where turnover for the half year to October 31
fell from Pounds 20.5m to Pounds 16.6m and pre-tax profits dropped from
Pounds 2.05m to Pounds 727,000.
