<HEADLINE>
FT  14 JAN 92 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
JOHANNESBURG drifted off Friday's record highs. The all-share index fell 11
to 3,633, while the industrial index fell 5 to 4,417. The all-gold index
lost 16 to 1,260 in line with a slight retreat in bullion prices. Vaal Reefs
fell R4 to R217.
</TEXT>
<PUB>The Financial Times
</PUB>
<PAGE>
London Page 33
