FT  14 JAN 92 / International Capital Markets: Belfox options trading
delayed
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By REUTER
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   BRUSSELS
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
TRADING of share options on Belfox, Belgium's futures and options exchange,
has been postponed, says Belfox general manager Mr Jos Schmitt, Reuter
reports from Brussels. It had been due to start in late January or early
February.
Mr Schmitt said the launch had been delayed because trading simulation had
not started yet in Belgium. A simulation was currently running in London, he
added.
